ast.name: Multi Mode Camera v0.1
ast.comment:
Multi mode camera.

1: self timer mode.
- tap screen or press camera button to start count down.
- tap again to cancel.
- countdown time can be set at setting menu.
- countdown voice in last 3 seconds.
2: quick picture mode.
- just tap or press camera button to take a picture.
3: cyclic mode.
- take pictures with specified interval time.
- tap screen or press camera button to start.
- tap again to stop.
- pictures will be combined to 9-in-1 image with timestamp.

*Pictures taken in this app will be low quality due to limitations of system environment.

decls.name: status
decls.comment: 0: main menu. 1: waiting start tap.  2: countdown.  3: last 3 sec. 4: take a quick shot. 9: quit.
